Nineteen people needed medical treatment and hundreds of firefighters deployed to fight a huge blaze at a Chinese chemical plant that produces a toxic chemical .
Authorities said initial tests suggested there had been no leaks from the plant 's three tanks of burning hydrocarbon liquids and no signs of contamination of the environment following the blast at Goure PX Plant in Zhangzhou , Fujian province .
